      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "Connors et al reported a 71-year-old male who was admitted with dyspnea due to BPVT and calcification of mitral valve prosthesis despite an international normalized ratio (INR) of 4; he recovered following redo MVR."
